reviews.text: It was DELICIOUS! The pigeon was delicious the skin was good and well cooked! The desert was excellent too! Staff are super friendly! I WILL come back here. Pigeon was one of the best I ever ate!

I experienced better food and ambience before but probably I am not a food expect. The sea food we ate was mostly black sos based and nothing fantastic. The best food was the mix grill crab and the. Famous dessert souffle also not that excellent.

I like their foods as well as the desert. I visit it from time to time. Ox tongues are incomparable by others throughout HK. I think I will rate it higher should their managers were more flexible and polite, while I found their waiters are generally kind.

This Cantonese-style restaurant is famous for several dishes which I've tried out. The Swiss wings (瑞士汁雞翼) were marinated with sweet soy sauce. Despite bring a very simple side dish, the wings are delicious. The stir-fried rice noodles  are served with sweet soy sauce (瑞士汁炒牛河) with a gravy-like texture which some might find too "wet". However this is fine with me. Unfortunately the chicken in the Macau-style Portuguese Chicken Rice (葡國雞飯) is a bit too dry and lacking of flavor.

food is ok, service is so-so,
quite expensive

reviews.text:
餐廳環境有懷舊feel，裝修都保持新淨，
餐牌內容豐富，食物出品都算合格，價格偏高少許，不過睇啱自已鐘食嘅懷舊豉油西餐，
都係值得嘅，因為現在冇邊間可以同佢雙比。
仲有服務幾好，有親切感，落單時會提示你，
夠食喇唔好再加馬，用餐時會主動同你換餐碟。
It was DELICIOUS! The pigeon was delicious the skin was good and well cooked! The desert was excellent too! Staff are super friendly! I WILL come back here. Pigeon was one of the best I ever ate!
